We have increased our campaigning among the indipendent capitalist class. [? if spm_in_government == 1 and mnlp_in_government == 1 and plfm_in_government == 0: We are currently in a coalition with {!<span style="color: #D3C24D;">liberal</span>!} parties, and this makes our campaigning efforts easier. ?][? if spm_in_government == 1 and mnlp_in_government == 0 and plfm_in_government == 1: We are currently in a coalition with {!<span style="color: #540808;">communist</span>!} parties, and this makes our campaigning more difficult. ?]

@capitalist_class
subtitle: -1 resources
choose-if: resources >= 1
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough resources.
view-if: peoples_party == 1
on-arrival: capitalist_class_spm += 1*(1-dissent); resources -= 1

We have increased our campaigning among the capitalist class. Since we are a marsist and socialist party, not much can be done to attract votes here, and only the privileged children of the Earth bourgeoisie represent a handful of winnable votes in this category.
